<div class="content-bg">
  <div id="main-right" class="main-right full">
    <div class="alt-item-head headerfull">
      <h2>Sign up</h2>
    </div>

      <div class="sign-up-left">
<%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name) :html => { :multipart => true }) do |f| %>
  <%= devise_error_messages! %>

  <p><%= f.label :name %><br />
  <%= f.text_field :name %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :email %><br />
  <%= f.email_field :email %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :about %><br />
  <%= f.text_area :about %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :avatar %><br />
    <%= f.file_field :avatar %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :password %><br />
  <%= f.password_field :password %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :password_confirmation %><br />
  <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation %></p>

  <p><%= f.submit "Sign up" %></p>
<% end %>

<%= render :partial => "devise/shared/links" %>

    <div class="clearall">
      </div>
      
      <div class="sign-up-right">
                    <h1>Jungol enables organizations to connect and collaborate to achieve common goals.</h1>

                    <p><b>Find a group</b>
                    Jungol makes it easy to find a group that can help you make a difference.  If you don’t see what you’re looking for, start your own group.  </p>

                    <p><b>Connect group-to-group</b>
                    The only site that lets your group link directly to other groups.  It’s like a facebook friend request for organizations.  </p>

                    <p><b>Collaborate on projects and events</b>
                    Use the power of interactive file-sharing, to-do lists, and discussion boards to make inter-organizational collaboration easy and efficient.</p>

                    <p><b>Increase your impact</b>
                    Achieve your target goals with less time and money by pooling resources and reducing duplication.”</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="clearall"></div>
  </div>
</div>